<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>TWZ</title><link>https://www.twz.com</link><description>防御世界的强大进攻。</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 08 Jul 2026 14:05:05 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>美国对伊朗进行打击，以报复过去 24 小时内霍尔木兹海峡航运遭受的多次袭击（更新）</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/u-s-strikes-iran-in-retaliation-for-multiple-attacks-on-shipping-in-strait-of-hormuz-over-last-24-hours</link><description>&lt;p&gt;周二早些时候，三艘油轮在霍尔木兹海峡遭到袭击，打破了本已岌岌可危的停火协议。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/u-s-strikes-iran-in-retaliation-for-multiple-attacks-on-shipping-in-strait-of-hormuz-over-last-24-hours"&gt;美国打击伊朗以报复过去 24 小时内霍尔木兹海峡航运遭受的多次袭击（已更新）的&lt;/a&gt;帖子首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;TWZ&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Jul 2026 01:52:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/u-s-strikes-iran-in-retaliation-for-multiple-attacks-on-shipping-in-strait-of-hormuz-over-last-24-hours</guid></item><item><title>B-52 战备状态不佳给新型 AGM-181A 核巡航导弹带来测试挑战</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/poor-b-52-readiness-creating-testing-challenges-for-new-agm-181a-nuclear-cruise-missile</link><description>&lt;p&gt;B-52 机队需要即将进行升级，需求量很大，但也遭受了悲惨的损失。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/poor-b-52-readiness-creating-testing-challenges-for-new-agm-181a-nuclear-cruise-missile"&gt;B-52 战备状态不佳给新型 AGM-181A 核巡航导弹带来测试挑战的&lt;/a&gt;帖子首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;TWZ&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 Jul 2026 23:46:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/poor-b-52-readiness-creating-testing-challenges-for-new-agm-181a-nuclear-cruise-missile</guid></item><item><title>航空母舰在哪里：2026 年 7 月 7 日</title><link>https://www.twz.com/sea/where-are-the-aircraft-carriers-july-7-2026</link><description>&lt;p&gt;随着美国加强其海军力量，拳师两栖部队在中东重新集结。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/sea/where-are-the-aircraft-carriers-july-7-2026"&gt;航空母舰在哪里：2026 年 7 月 7 日&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;TWZ&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 Jul 2026 22:34:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/sea/where-are-the-aircraft-carriers-july-7-2026</guid></item><item><title>非洲之角海盗袭击事件激增</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/pirate-attacks-on-shipping-off-the-horn-of-africa-spike</link><description>&lt;p&gt;由于航运业刚刚从与伊朗的战争和红海的战斗中恢复过来，胡塞武装很可能以海盗的形式支持自己的代理人。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/pirate-attacks-on-shipping-off-the-horn-of-africa-spike"&gt;非洲之角海盗袭击&lt;/a&gt;事件首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;TWZ&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 Jul 2026 18:59:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/pirate-attacks-on-shipping-off-the-horn-of-africa-spike</guid></item><item><title>中国导弹试验基地发现神秘矩形“发射井”</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/mysterious-rectangle-silos-emerge-at-sprawling-chinese-missile-test-base</link><description>&lt;p&gt;具有大型矩形可伸缩屋顶的结构可能表明中国可以更广泛地部署新的战略能力。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/mysterious-rectangle-silos-emerge-at-sprawling-chinese-missile-test-base"&gt;在庞大的中国导弹试验基地发现的神秘矩形“发射井”的&lt;/a&gt;帖子首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;TWZ&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 Jul 2026 18:57:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/mysterious-rectangle-silos-emerge-at-sprawling-chinese-missile-test-base</guid></item><item><title>北约选择 Saab GlobalEye 取代老化的 E-3 预警机机队</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/nato-picks-saab-globaleye-to-replace-aging-e-3-awacs-fleet</link><description>&lt;p&gt;在收购 GlobalEye 的同时，北约还宣布了一系列涵盖无人机、海上巡逻机、加油机和运输机的能力。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;北约&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/nato-picks-saab-globaleye-to-replace-aging-e-3-awacs-fleet"&gt;选择 Saab GlobalEye 取代老化的 E-3 预警机机队&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 Jul 2026 16:23:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/nato-picks-saab-globaleye-to-replace-aging-e-3-awacs-fleet</guid></item><item><title>VH-92 爱国者获得花岗岩白宫直升机停机坪将最终让 VH-3D 海王退役</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/vh-92-patriot-getting-granite-white-house-helipad-will-finally-allow-vh-3d-sea-king-to-retire</link><description>&lt;p&gt;在白宫草坪上着陆数十年后，“海军陆战队一号”将在直升机停机坪上运行，特朗普称 VH-92 的制造商正在为此付费。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;后&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/vh-92-patriot-getting-granite-white-house-helipad-will-finally-allow-vh-3d-sea-king-to-retire"&gt;VH-92 爱国者获得花岗岩白宫直升机停机坪将最终允许 VH-3D 海王退役&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;TWZ&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 Jul 2026 00:32:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/vh-92-patriot-getting-granite-white-house-helipad-will-finally-allow-vh-3d-sea-king-to-retire</guid></item><item><title>朝鲜护卫舰上机枪数量可笑</title><link>https://www.twz.com/sea/north-koreas-frigate-bristles-with-a-comical-number-of-machine-guns</link><description>&lt;p&gt;朝鲜的Kang Kon军舰在为金公恩举行的示威活动中进行了全面的机枪扫射。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/sea/north-koreas-frigate-bristles-with-a-comical-number-of-machine-guns"&gt;朝鲜护卫舰上配备数量可笑的机枪的&lt;/a&gt;帖子首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;TWZ&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Jul 2026 23:18:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/sea/north-koreas-frigate-bristles-with-a-comical-number-of-machine-guns</guid></item><item><title>加拿大选择德国 212 型潜艇来满足急需的舰队更新需求</title><link>https://www.twz.com/sea/canada-picks-german-type-212-submarine-for-badly-needed-fleet-renewal</link><description>&lt;p&gt;此次采购 12 艘舰艇是加拿大有史以来最大的国防采购之一，标志着加拿大与欧洲盟国加强军事合作的重大转变。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/sea/canada-picks-german-type-212-submarine-for-badly-needed-fleet-renewal"&gt;加拿大挑选德国 212 型潜艇用于急需的舰队更新的&lt;/a&gt;帖子首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;TWZ&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Jul 2026 19:59:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/sea/canada-picks-german-type-212-submarine-for-badly-needed-fleet-renewal</guid></item><item><title>没有爱国者拦截机，乌克兰无法击落任何袭击基辅的弹道导弹</title><link>https://www.twz.com/land/out-of-patriot-interceptors-ukraine-cant-down-any-ballistic-missiles-striking-kyiv</link><description>&lt;p&gt;乌克兰正试图让盟友捐赠更多的爱国者拦截弹，而此时导弹的供应量非常低且需求极大。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/land/out-of-patriot-interceptors-ukraine-cant-down-any-ballistic-missiles-striking-kyiv"&gt;没有爱国者拦截机，乌克兰无法击落任何袭击基辅的弹道导弹，&lt;/a&gt;该帖子首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;TWZ&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Jul 2026 19:05:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/land/out-of-patriot-interceptors-ukraine-cant-down-any-ballistic-missiles-striking-kyiv</guid></item></channel></rss>